/>\n再儲返一兩年錢先補返擺酒<br />\n慢慢搵到每人20k+就開始舒服"},{"pid":"a79da09eff0a014e99355edb698f46a9ed4073ba","tid":146410,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加埋26k 租新界區夠住</blockquote><br />\n港島撚真係離唔開港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錢就要將就㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算住新界，人工一半都去左租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c0cae61093a18355190d3ae65112b26c1921cb","tid":146410,"uid":28660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加埋26k 租新界區夠住</blockquote><br />\n港島撚真係離唔開港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錢就要將就㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算住新界，人工一半都去左租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架"},{"pid":"44331a93105cfdcc88b95e7d98bfff367cb52d19","tid":146410,"uid":3976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:12:34.000Z","msg":"唔食野 7個月儲到首期啦"},{"pid":"752a8617cb03a3ba9a8a4936ffb7e33e54ab2164","tid":146410,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔食野 7個月儲到首期啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53a78f6d368913dafac76d7957fdc4ed57f9f38","tid":146410,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加埋26k 租新界區夠住</blockquote><br />\n港島撚真係離唔開港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錢就要將就㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算住新界，人工一半都去左租金<img src=\"/assets/face